org.jets3t.service.multi.event
Class LookupACLEvent

java.lang.Object
  org.jets3t.service.multi.event.ServiceEvent
      org.jets3t.service.multi.event.LookupACLEvent

public class LookupACLEvent
extends ServiceEvent

Multi-threaded service event fired by ThreadedStorageService.getObjectACLs(String, StorageObject[]).

EVENT_IN_PROGRESS events include an array of the StorageObjects whose ACLs have been retrieved since the last progress event was fired. These objects are available via getObjectsWithACL().

EVENT_CANCELLED events include an array of the StorageObjects whose ACLs had not been retrieved before the operation was cancelled. These objects are available via getCancelledObjects().
